data.text: We were delighted to host a visit from our friends in the Royal Netherlands Air Force (RNLAF), led by Chief of the Air Staff, Lieutenant General Dennis Luyt, who dropped in to take a closer look at the fantastic work our teams are doing to drive availability of their C-130 fleet.
